---
title: Chinese Garlic Beef Stir-Fry with Snow Peas
description: If you’re a long-time lover of the signature mix of sweet, spicy and salty, then you are going to go nuts for this simple stir-fry. Combine lightly marinated beef with courgette, carrot and crisp snow peas, for a colourful array of flavours of textures.
